Welcome to our application! Before using our services, please read the following Privacy Policy carefully to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
1. Information Collection and Use
We may collect the following types of information to provide and improve our services:
● Personal Identifiable Information: We may collect your name, email address, contact information, or other personal information that you voluntarily provide.
●We do not collect facial data, and the server does not save facial data.
● Usage Data: When you access and use our application, we may automatically collect information about your device, operating system, and application usage to help us optimize the user experience.
2. Information Protection
We commit to taking appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, please be aware that data transmission and storage over the internet cannot be guaranteed to be 100% secure, so we cannot ensure the absolute security of information.
3. Information Use
We may use your personal information to:
● Provide you with the requested services.
● Communicate with you, including responding to your questions and feedback.
● Improve our application and services.
4. Information Sharing
We will not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share information with third parties in the following circumstances:
● According to legal requirements or government requests.
● To protect our rights, property, or safety, and to prevent fraud or imminent harm.
● With your consent.
5. Privacy Choices
You can choose not to provide personal information, but this may limit your access to certain features and services. You may also withdraw your consent at any time, stopping our collection and use of your personal information.
6. Privacy Policy Changes
We may update the Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices and legal requirements. The updated Privacy Policy will be posted within the application and will notify you before it takes effect.
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding the Privacy Policy, please feel free to contact us. Contact Email: help@apptrainings.com.
8. "Policy on Private Information and Refund Processing:
To process your refund request, Apple needs permission to gather pertinent personal data for review purposes. This may include your Apple ID, purchasing records, account activity logs, subscription details, payment verification (excluding full credit card details), the reason for refunding, and device-specific information.
This data is for processing your refund request only and abides by Apple's privacy policies. By applying for a refund, you agree to these terms. Thank you for using our App."


Please note that by using our application, you agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy.